#### Extending the AI
=======
The game starts with White's turn.

Click on a piece to select it, and then click on a valid destination to move.

The AI will play its move after you make yours.

Play continues until checkmate, stalemate, or resignation.

Development

Key Functionalities

Game Initialization: The chessboard is dynamically generated using JavaScript.

Turn Switching: Alternates between White and Black turns.

Move Validation: Implements move rules for all chess pieces.

Check and Checkmate: Validates check and checkmate conditions after every move.

Extending the AI
>>>>>>> parent of 9910a9e (Implement titles and text formatting)

To improve or customize the AI:

Enhance the move evaluation logic in script.js.

